        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Fair Drug Prices for Kids Act</b></p> <p>This bill allows states to apply the requirements of the Medicaid Drug Rebate Program to covered outpatient drugs under the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP).</p>]]>
        </text>
